Varavig, the simplest way to organize Agile Projects, is based on Rails and backbone.js
Varavig is a product of IIPIR developed by Roberto Gil and Pablo Pazos.

how to run dev server:
 $ play run varavig

how to deploy to gae:
outside the projet root folder execute:
 $ play war varavig -o varavig-war
 $ /appengine-java-sdk-1.4.2/bin/appcfg.sh update varavig-war